,"msg":"隻隻坐十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb3e3f4bce272cd7a7b3f939fc48c5bed235a9ee","tid":1398290,"uid":144541,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T18:12:31.000Z","msg":"無咩可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />律政司點會告自己人"},{"pid":"69a46664987d57e0bc463ffe509292e3fb472a73","tid":1398290,"uid":109433,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T18:12:37.000Z","msg":"律政司未以公眾利益唔提告囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"877c3b08f55b735806a4cdf1d821422f214c7f37","tid":1398290,"uid":132949,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T18:13:03.000Z","msg":"但係搵邊個去告佢地?"},{"pid":"9650f49965e36f4e40b8843588dfadf058877b71","tid":1398290,"uid":24779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T18:14:08.000Z","msg":"有精力諗下點幫義士好過啦，啲狗返緊工點畀你拗到佢係非法集結呢"},{"pid":"f232137506fc634bd6f150cfd228d18f91af8c4f","tid":1398290,"uid":194169,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T18:14:09.000Z","msg":"告到的話，佢哋一早坐緊監啦<br />\n問題係邊個負責檢控呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31a24948d75546e8e2e35fba2aad628e1f1bbd28","tid":1398290,"uid":122083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T18:16:24.000Z","msg":"唔拘捕 唔檢控 唔搜證<br />\n全部都係我啲人 你點告啊"},{"pid":"2e3e5416474a7aa46d13f3bb11ce918303553dee","tid":1398290,"uid":280192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T19:26:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cd092ab926e6bc6e6fcd5e6afc9fa8ee2820b9f1","tid":1398290,"uid":55233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T19:46:29.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"65070a2e846f2a01469075acef800b231956ba4e","tid":1398290,"uid":44090,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T19:56:03.000Z","msg":"提私人檢控？<br />\n但係點做搜證？<br />\n但係做到應該make到noise"},{"pid":"bf02792c97398b9726d7fa0910d14f08939ae6e4","tid":1398290,"uid":25055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T20:00:46.000Z","msg":"點解外國既司法部係獨立<br />\n<br />\n香港律政司完全係聽政府命令<br />\n<br />\n香港重光後一定要改革律政司"},{"pid":"103348734dca67f0e170b6712db36ebe71aeafd2","tid":1398290,"uid":280192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T02:15:56.000Z","msg":"私人撿控最困難在於搜證，但暴動罪本身並不難搜證，理論上現場如果是暴動，留在現場人士就算參與暴動罪。<br />\n<br />\n那警方如果已定性了現場是暴動，餘下的只是證實他們在現場，並做了超出職務範圍應做的事(如他們威脅記者阻差辦公一樣，在職也可犯法)，甚至警方根本是現場破壞社會安寧本身的源頭。這變相等於獨立調查。"},{"pid":"42685f56750c59ab23d438144eec187a6c887fc6","tid":1398290,"uid":260367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T02:25:13.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"8a92dd6b9b81956487da4daf62c59c1896bb0a65","tid":1398290,"uid":44090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"103348734dca67f0e170b6712db36ebe71aeafd2","tid":1398290,"uid":280192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T02:15:56.000Z","msg":"私人撿控最困難在於搜證，但暴動罪本身並不難搜證，理論上現場如果是暴動，留在現場人士就算參與暴動罪。<br />\n<br />\n那警方如果已定性了現場是暴動，餘下的只是證實他們在現場，並做了超出職務範圍應做的事(如他們威脅記者阻差辦公一樣，在職也可犯法)，甚至警方根本是現場破壞社會安寧本身的源頭。這變相等於獨立調查。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T04:29:25.000Z","msg":"但係暴動base on非法集結<br />\n首先要proof到班狗呢樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}